      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WITHOUT A TRACE (4) is a well performed dog and winner of 18 races who is worth forgiving after finishing out of the placings at Dubbo (35.01). Is yet to taste defeat at this course and distance. Has a solid record from this box including two wins and a minor placing. Ready to return to form. MEPUNGA LARA (1) is in hot form after clocking a convincing 41.75 victory two back then followed up with a 41.86 win at this track over 720m last time. Expecting another bold showing. MAGPIE HECTOR (7) isn't a quick beginner but comes home hard, winding up to score two back then finishing on strongly last time when third (34.88) in a NG at Dubbo. Has a strong record here at this journey including two wins. Yet to miss the placings in eight runs from this box, including two wins. Expected to be in this for a long way. DERRY (2) should bounce back after an unplaced effort here recently.",
